{"tid":509273,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple玩完！A股概念股大跌 至停版！鄭州廠緊急暫停招工","createTime":"2017-12-25T06:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T16:15:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"baa87278145aa8bcc57e69636a9aaeadaa145c52","tid":509273,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"新浪財經訊 12月25日消息，剛過完&ldquo;黑五&rdquo;銷售旺季又迎聖誕假日之際，iPhone X再度傳出負面消息，蘋果產業鏈相關個股周一均紛紛下挫，截止發稿，科森科技(27.530, -1.37, -4.74%)跌停，報26.01元，藍思科技(28.590, -2.46, -7.92%)、安潔科技(25.810, -2.69, -9.44%)、創聯電子跌幅均超7%，共達電聲(8.440, -0.37, -4.20%)、超聲電子(13.480, -1.01, -6.97%)、歌爾股份(16.880, -0.66, -3.76%)等相關概念股均紛紛下挫。<br />\n<br />\n　　消息面：<br />\n<br />\n　　耶誕節當天，台灣經濟 日報援引供應鏈消息稱，iPhone X銷售不如預期，蘋果下修明年首季銷量預估，從原訂單季5000萬部大減四成，至3000萬部，減幅超乎市場此前的預期。<br />\n<br />\n　　報導還稱，獨家組裝iPhone X的鴻海富士康旗下鄭州工廠緊急宣佈，自12月25日起全面暫停招工，沒有出現之前生產旺季時的連續加速招工現象。<br />\n<br />\n　　本月中旬，市場傳出蘋果公司對代工廠原本的追單反轉為砍單，公司大砍針對台積電的A11處理器訂單，明年第一季度A11的投片量比本季銳減三成。有分析推斷，iPhoneX明年第一季度訂單量也會隨之下調30%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/gujiayidong/2017-12-25/doc-ifypxrpp3790984.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.com.cn%2Fstock%2Fgujiayidong%2F2017-12-25%2Fdoc-ifypxrpp3790984.shtml&d=tChkqxY43xZa1fhjETCzmrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e93cb9e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/gujiayidong/2017-12-25/doc-ifypxrpp3790984.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"27de28350dd45247f280acde74254509d9a9fcee","tid":509273,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e7910d0b17ce2e9322d1551c76fb2f62bf9d96","tid":509273,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite